data.description: Welcome to Norfolk Dr in Temple, TX! This Modern Farmhouse-style home boasts over 3000 sqft, 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an office, and a bonus room with a closet. The home's tall ceilings and open concept create a spacious feel, while natural wood accents and gold highlights add warmth and elegance. Come experience this stunning home for yourself! Builder is offering $10,000 builder credit towards closing costs or rate buy down with accepted offer.
